data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Northern Heights subdivision! This charming 3 bed 2 bath residence offers the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and city convenience, situated just minutes away from downtown Waynesville. Step inside to discover an inviting open floorplan, ideal for both daily living and entertaining. The kitchen features a stylish island and gleaming stainless steel appliances, creating a chef's paradise. Retreat to the spacious master suite boasting a luxurious bathroom with a large shower, offering the ultimate relaxation experience. Outside, enjoy the privacy of a fenced yard with a covered patio and pergola, perfect for enjoying the outdoors in any weather. Additional highlights include a convenient storage shed, completing this picture-perfect home. Don't miss your chance to make this oasis yours! Schedule your showing today.
